                            voices</font> <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

                            acoustic guitar (nylon strings)&nbsp;</font> <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

                            mid and high registers of church organ&nbsp;</font> 

                            <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

                            panflute&nbsp;</font> <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

