                            and: applause</font></font><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br>

                            </font></b></p>

                        </blockquote>

                      </td>

                      <td width="181" height="265" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 

                        <blockquote> 

                          <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="5">piano&nbsp;</font> 

                            <font size="5" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

                            electronic bas&nbsp;</font> <font size="5" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

                            synthesizer&nbsp;</font> <font size="5" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>

